message.text:
UPDATE: My Maomao is now reserved for a fellow furmom.

Looking for a loving home for my maomao, Missy. 🐾

Hi, Tams! I’m looking for a new furparent for my baby Missy, a 7-year-old pure Persian cat born on June 27, 2018. She is fully vaccinated (rabies shots renewed last February) and healthy. She will be given a dose of Advocate spot-on to be protected from other cats before adoption. 

Due to personal reasons and upcoming work/study commitments, I can no longer provide her with the stable environment she deserves. I want her to be in a home where she’ll continue to be loved and cared for.

I'm willing to give my baby for adoption for a lower price, 8,000; 9,500 with her stainless litter box (2k original price and in great condition) and elevated ceramic food bowls (700+ original price w/ minor defects). Payment is not urgent, can be done through 2-5 gives.

Releasing date: September 18-20, 2025 
Pick-up Area: Cubao

If you’re interested, kindly send me a message. I would also greatly appreciate occasional visits and updates about her, since she has always been such an important part of my life. 💛
